Package: rsunflo
Title: Tools for phenotyping, simulating and modelling with the SUNFLO crop
    model
Description: A set of tools for working with the SUNFLO crop model at different
    steps. input data : computing genotype-specific parameters and creating
    climatic files. simulation : designing virtual experiments and
    multi-simulation. modelling : tracking the variation of prediction capacity
    along with model development.
Version: 0.1
Author: Pierre Casadebaig <pierre.casadebaig@toulouse.inra.fr>
Maintainer: Pierre Casadebaig <pierre.casadebaig@toulouse.inra.fr>
Imports:
    reshape2,
    plyr,
    ggplot2
Suggests:
    rvle
License: GPL
Collate:
    'phenotyping.R'
    'simulation.R'
    'tools.R'
    'modelling.R'
